{"tid":965823,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"東方：國泰跪低補鑊　半折頭等商務混合機票全有效","createTime":"2019-01-02T10:45:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-02T15:35:22.000Z","uid":41404,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"ff3fd34ed3f53690f3fff0344981b9f8c9b908a3","tid":965823,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T10:45:15.000Z","msg":"國泰跪低補鑊　半折頭等商務混合機票全有效<br />\n01月02日(三) 18:00<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\">因管理不善在全球最佳航空公司排名榜節節下跌、洩漏940萬客戶個人資料的國泰航空</span></ins></strong>，日前被揭發疑似網站及訂票系統出錯，出現「半折頭等商務混合機票」的優惠。國泰今日(2日)在其Facebook及Twitter貼文，向所有成功購票者跪低補鑊，承認所有頭等及商務機票均有效，並標記(Hashtag)稱「從小就學會錯就要認」，又稱是次僅為新年放閃推廣計劃。不過，國泰重申，其網站及訂票系統運作正常，只是輸入出錯才會出現是次事件。<br />\n<br />\n有外國博客前日(12月31日)分享一篇名為1000美元購買國泰頭等機票的文章，部分航線例如越南河內經香港轉機至加拿大溫哥華或美國紐約，出現頭等、商務機票混合大優惠，往返機票連稅只需988美元(約7687港元)及1445美元(約11,242港元)，相等於正價機票約5%。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190102/bkn-20190102180051931-0102_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190102%2Fbkn-20190102180051931-0102_00822_001.html&d=mQHFsxKfgzE2mw2WxC2sD6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=4caed086\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190102/bkn-20190102180051931-0102_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"7fdcc2f0c1a4c72d416f8a9c6baab2c1902c623f","tid":965823,"uid":173930,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T10:47:21.000Z","msg":"姐係原價要二十萬？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e7b8e3d2af8cdbdcbd30aa4f58b412bb9bec9eb","tid":965823,"uid":216709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T10: